      <scopecontent id="aspace_34b112eb1c0a4fe5ec0fb5577b59bd64">
         <head>Content Description</head>
         <p>This collection consists of set and costume designs by Stephen O. Saxe, photographs of theatrical set designs and performances, photographs of the Saxe family, and other papers including printed materials, and writings. Also includes a set design by Robert Edmond Jones.</p>
      </scopecontent>
